Chelsea Ricketts https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chelsea_Ricketts 0 Chelsea Ricketts (born October 29, 1989) is an American film and television actress. She played in the movie Crooked Arrows as Nadie Logan. She is from Katy, Texas and is a 2008 graduate of Seven Lakes High School.
